<h2 class="section-header">About</h2>

<article>

<p id="about-p">The <span id="tcp-name">Trans Composers Project</span> celebrates and uplifts trangender, nonbinary, and genderqueer composers by providing them opportunities to connect, share, learn, and grow with other trans, queer, and allied musicians.</p>

</article>
